<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-row>
      <v-col cols="3">
        <v-card outlined>
        </v-card>
      </v-col>
      <v-col cols="9">
        <v-card outlined class="profile_card">
          <v-row class="text-left">
            <v-col cols="3">
              ID Number
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="9">
              {{idnum}}
            </v-col>
          </v-row>

          <v-row class="text-left"> 
            <v-col cols="3">
              Name
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="9" >
              {{name}}
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
          
          <v-row class="text-left"> 
            <v-col cols="3">
              Email
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="9" >
              {{email}}
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
          
          <v-row class="text-left"> 
            <v-col cols="3">
              Password
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="9" >
              {{password}}
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
          
          <v-row class="text-left"> 
            <v-col cols="3">
              Position
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="9" >
              {{position}}
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
          
          <v-row class="text-left">   
            <v-col cols="3">
              Campus
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="9" >
              {{campus}}
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
        </v-card>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>

</script>

<style>
.profile_card{
  padding-left: 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.profile_card v-col{
  border: 1px; 
}
</style>
